NoFileToUpload: Nothing to upload, select a file first
VersionNamingExtTooltip:
1. Download the JSON file with the extended revision sequences that are already declared.
2. In the JSON file, add, modify, or remove the extended revision sequences of your choice.
3. Upload the updated file.
VersionNamingExtTypeHeader: Assign Extended Revision Sequence to Types
VersionNamingExtTypeTooltip:
1. Expand type tree in Type column.
2. Select type you want to set or reset the sequence.
3. Select in Extended Revision Sequence column the sequence to set.
VersionNamingLogTypeHeader: Assign Revision Sequence Logic to Types
VersionNamingLogTypeTooltip:
1. Expand type tree in Type column.
2. Select type you want to set or reset the sequence.
3. Select in Revision Sequence Logic column the sequence to set.
